org.apache.poi.util

Class RLEDecompressingInputStream

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.InputStream
      • org.apache.poi.util.RLEDecompressingInputStream
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Closeable, java.lang.AutoCloseable

    public class RLEDecompressingInputStream
extends java.io.InputStream
    Wrapper of InputStream which provides Run Length Encoding (RLE) decompression on the fly. Uses MS-OVBA decompression algorithm. See http://download.microsoft.com/download/2/4/8/24862317-78F0-4C4B-B355-C7B2C1D997DB/[MS-OVBA].pdf(${t_72cb408b4db14a169ad5623a16e51980})
